title: Supercars.Exposed-Speed2008-L.A.Rally.Exotics.LowRiders
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Features a Los Angeles car rally featuring both supercars/exotics and classic low riders.  Cars featured: Lamborghinis, Ferraris, Porsches, Ford GT, and lots of american low riders, like a 1967 Chevy Impala.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.
